strings.Value: "Remember when we said we saw a spy from the {g|Technic League}Technic League{/g} in the capital? We should have hustled. While we were packing, the scum up and vanished."

"Remember how we found out about that {g|Technic League}Technic League{/g} lair, where Janush had dug in? Scouts report the wretches left the kingdom. It's too late to catch them — they're probably already in {g|Numeria}Numeria{/g} by now."

"I guess we'll never know what the {g|Technic League}Technic League{/g} wanted... Now if only they'd never come back. I don't think for a minute they'll just leave us alone — but we'll probably never get such a lucky chance to take them unawares again."
